{"tid":499430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果呢個世界 「數學」或者「語文」其中一樣要消失，你會揀邊樣？","createTime":"2017-12-14T19:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T23:38:19.000Z","uid":137840,"like":45,"dislike":64,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d009ac07a90abe5c827b2e8566c29c382b8dd6","tid":499430,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:35:33.000Z","msg":"如果冇左語文既話 人與人之間就會溝通唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係如果冇左數學 科技基本上唔會存在係呢個世界 唔會有燈 唔會有手機...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果假設有一日 兩者其一要消失<br />\n唔知大家會揀邊樣消失呢？<br />\n（投個票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：語文<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：數學"},{"pid":"9128cccce4cbea59df6693bc044d5b77628eb55e","tid":499430,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5297a5a20180997bae7e2b443d60958fc72381","tid":499430,"uid":144312,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:37:58.000Z","msg":"自己消失"},{"pid":"51e43297d328a05b0111e9b81f7795a2b027aba7","tid":499430,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己消失</blockquote><br />\n做咩咁睇唔開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112ebe11f629155dfd375248001404e8bd235b8a","tid":499430,"uid":137840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:43:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"5cf9575ee8b6c0af8e79f27561361421e547e3af","tid":499430,"uid":155591,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:45:14.000Z","msg":"數學唔係已經係語言既一種咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cd273061ee517eb52f47fa453351b92f76b327","tid":499430,"uid":4288,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:47:13.000Z","msg":"語文可以消失，本身覺得數學科學對人類既貢獻重要過語文，而且就算話文消失左，我地可以用數字去交流溝通，用數字去代替文字黎溝通，例如12代表你 、13代表我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47278b57d4d4c709a279c60c5cb7f77cc5bebe12","tid":499430,"uid":62133,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:48:11.000Z","msg":"無語言得數學呢個世界得返機械人？<br />\n<br />\n係咁我寧願得語言，起碼有血有肉，<br />\n你睇動物都唔識數學無iPhone 用咪又係食訓扑野。"},{"pid":"cdf40e06a0663471fcdd84ba2add3761ea18a138","tid":499430,"uid":139139,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T19:51:07.000Z","msg":"諗下原始人<br />\n都係有語文出現先<br />\n數學係由語文產生<br />\n因為有語文先至有概念<br />\n有概念先至會思考<br />\n先至會計算<br />\n<br />\n冇咗語文冇咗溝通<br />\n係會令個世界運作唔到<br />\n法例丶交易丶生活嘅所有野<br />\n都需要用到語文<br />\n人係群體生物"},{"pid":"c773a5426a7d3ed4c6cd6158caeb42a335f259af","tid":499430,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"af394b0c6316d0dc0cf659acf6dee2d4d1adb72d","tid":499430,"uid":7225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:15:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果冇左語文既話 人與人之間就會溝通唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係如果冇左數學 科技基本上唔會存在係呢個世界 唔會有燈 唔會有手機...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果假設有一日 兩者其一要消失<br />\n唔知大家會揀邊樣消失呢？<br />\n（投個票啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：語文<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：數學</blockquote><br />\n語言唔單止係用嚟溝通，語言係文明嘅根本。<br />\n你睇嘅書留到落嚟嘅所有知識都係靠語文嚟記載，無語文又何來哲學？無哲學又何來數學呢？<br />\n而其實數字都係一種符號語言，如果人類唔賦予意義比啲數字，佢係唔會有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡單啲講，鬼佬睇中文數字，佢唔識中文唔會明，但對於中國人嚟講，我哋可以用中文數字嚟計數，而點樣先令鬼佬學識睇中文數字？就係靠語言。"},{"pid":"d5f0ba9c2038fa247947c83921e4a36096133c61","tid":499430,"uid":7225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果發展到可以心靈感應，就唔需要語言了</blockquote><br />\n其實心靈感應只係另一種語言，因為你係Transfer緊Info。"},{"pid":"1aadd2ba89cec5bfc786b7e01d96b35aa92bda2e","tid":499430,"uid":3773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T21:28:42.000Z","msg":"冇咗語文根本連知識傳承都做唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過求其冇一樣影響都係極大㗎喇"},{"pid":"29155263d7b00a9e1d0188eaa6bcf326719eae6f","tid":499430,"uid":111789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T22:36:39.000Z","msg":"兩樣都好重要喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是但一樣無左的話都改變成個世界<br />\nBTW如果無左你的屎忽腦就對世界進步再踏出新一步"},{"pid":"d7486a3876017c45d748acf21858928845dd9f2b","tid":499430,"uid":123296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T22:55:38.000Z","msg":"無語文，何來數學"},{"pid":"66322eb2c65b5aea836b695e753499e968cbf5d2","tid":499430,"uid":35951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:20:38.000Z","msg":"why not both <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22907c54c9eb38ab6c538012b7ca41e07ad5cf91","tid":499430,"uid":133714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T23:38:19.000Z","msg":"唔明有咩好投<br />\non9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}